title.narrative: Mekong Delta Transport Infrastructure Development Project

description.narrative: The project development objective is to to improve access to markets by businesses, farmers and the poor with lower logisitics costs resulting from the alleviation of key physical and institutional bottlenecks of the main transport corridors in the Mekong Delta region.
